name: Real Moon
description:
The objective of this model is the greatest possible realism in balance with beauty, being able to generate SFW and NSFW images.

The anime version of this model.

Baked in VAE

I usually use

  • Clip skip: 1

  • Upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+

  • Denoising strength: 0.4

  • Hires steps: same as the Sampling steps

Recommended Loras: Detail Tweaker, Better Portrait Lighting

Recommended embeddings: bad-artist, EasyNegativeV2
